# Title: Antivirus Filter Driver Disallowed On Dev Drive - Registry
# Author: @kostastsale, Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-11-05
# Level: high
# Description: Detects activity that indicates a user disabling the ability for Antivirus mini filter to inspect a "Dev Drive".
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.defense-impairment, attack.t1685
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/registry/registry_set/registry_set_devdrv_disallow_antivirus_filter.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Unlikely

Details="DWORD (0x00000000)" TargetObject="*\\FilterManager\\FltmgrDevDriveAllowAntivirusFilter"